                                <condition>
                                    <p>There are many traces of wear and the bottom right corners
                                        are often darker than the rest of the leaves. </p>
                                    <p>The bottom outer corners of ff. <locus from="29r" to="31v"
                                            >29-31</locus> are excised. </p>
                                    <p>There is damage due to moisture at the outer edge of many of
                                        the leaves. </p>
                                    <p>The parchment has a few small holes.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
